description: Java entity class representing lounge booking details, mapped to the 'lounge_bookings' database table.

classes.name: LoungeBookingEntity
classes.description: Entity class for lounge booking information, including booking ID, lounge pass count, creation timestamp, and update timestamp.

methods.name: getBookingId
methods.description: Returns the UUID of the lounge booking.

methods.name: setBookingId
methods.description: Sets the UUID of the lounge booking.

methods.name: getLoungePassCount
methods.description: Returns the number of lounge passes booked.

methods.name: setLoungePassCount
methods.description: Sets the number of lounge passes booked.

methods.name: getCreatedAt
methods.description: Returns the timestamp when the booking was created.

methods.name: setCreatedAt
methods.description: Sets the timestamp when the booking was created.

methods.name: getUpdatedAt
methods.description: Returns the timestamp when the booking was last updated.

methods.name: setUpdatedAt
methods.description: Sets the timestamp when the booking was last updated.
